# Generated by XcodeGen from project.yml — never edit it directly, and never
# commit it. Run `xcodegen generate` after cloning, and after any project.yml
# change. Tracking it produced a large meaningless diff on every regeneration.
# (This supersedes ignoring project.pbxproj alone, which left the rest of the
# bundle — schemes, workspace data — still tracked.)
Hybridge.xcodeproj/

# Xcode
DerivedData/
build/
*.xcuserstate
xcuserdata/
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM
*.dSYM.zip

# Swift Package Manager
.swiftpm/
.build/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Protocol dumps captured from real hardware. These are configuration-file
# (0x0800) reads, so they include the body profile — real age, gender, height
# and weight. Keep them locally as byte oracles; never publish them.
*.bin
# ...but the watchface/widget blobs that ship in the app are not dumps.
!Resources/**/*.bin

# Scratch archives (e.g. the design-handoff export, a duplicate of
# design_handoff_dashboard/).
*.zip

# Build and test logs
*.log
AppStore/Metadata
AppStore/Screenshots/fr-FR
AppStore/Screenshots/es-ES
AppStore/Screenshots/de-DE
.claude
